values.description: URL for your Tableau Server or Online environment. e.g. http://myTableauServer.com
URL for the version of the REST API you want to use. e.g. /api/exp or /api/3.1
Name of the site to use. There should not be any hyphens. e.g. mysite
Username to be used to sign-in.
Password to be used to sign-in.
The ID of the site being used with the REST API. This will be automatically set if the accompanying Postman collection is used for sign-in.
The token to be used for all REST API calls. This will be passed in the 'X-Tableau-Auth' header. This will be automatically set if the accompanying Postman collection is used for sign-in.
